ps://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"8297cb48896e259787c23f7c1a74172590bca6d5","tid":1396319,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:15:26.000Z","msg":"！"},{"pid":"d69bbb74d24064ff7b002509f8598ab07fe8ea61","tid":1396319,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"浸成日講同中國友好啦，然後話貿易談判有進展 ，結果咪次次加關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大篇幅講香港，證明佢都有放入眼內，雖然唔知佢會點做，但絕對唔會唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論都係自己香港自己救，浸有機會就會送土共一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光</span></span>"},{"pid":"935c10a6c8d5ed673afbd9ef3da260a1b72bab73","tid":1396319,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"絕對唔可以完全靠曬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b9835bb8514d822b51167f0e3c84054aa139b8","tid":1396319,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"證明方向正確。<br />\n佢哋真係好撚驚美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以將港共做緊d仆街嘢繼續向外宣揚，成效有幾多都好。"}]}